items.name: Brutal Restraint
explicitMods:
Denoted service of 6167 dekhara in the akhara of Balbala
Passives in radius are Conquered by the Maraketh
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: They believed themselves the most ordered, but that tradition turned their forests to salt.

items.name: Watcher's Eye
explicitMods: 10% increased Movement Speed while affected by Grace
Impales you inflict last 2 additional Hits while using Pride
+15% chance to Suppress Spell Damage while affected by Grace
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature
they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating,
and one by one, they became a part of it.

items.name: Forbidden Flame
explicitMods: Allocates Brutal Fervour if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flesh
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The minds of those studied utterly by the Cleansing Fire
continue to think and dream and beg for silence...

items.name: Forbidden Flesh
explicitMods: Allocates Brutal Fervour if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flame
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
